  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were-- the Gestapo posted a detail in the street for my sister, they had her picture from the identity card.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the people where she-- where she went down into the house through the roof-- which were total strangers, and they were good people-- and they told her to dress as a man.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They gave her a man's suit and a hat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were looking for a woman, and she was dressed as a man, and that's how she escaped that area, that neighborhood, where they were looking for her.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she went into hiding with another sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, coming back to-- to the camp, so my sister was outside, and she had the opportunity to find out things and to send us food into the camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They-- from the clandestine Palestinian office, the head of that office, was a name-- his name was Szatan.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was from the leftist Zionist movement, and he was himself, on that list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was outside, and he got in touch with my sister, or she got in touch with him, and he told that we are on the list, and that the list has a value.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A few days before the transport, which-- which was the 26th transport from Mechelen-- each transport had about 1,000 Jews-- we was scheduled for the 26th transport.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A few days before the transport, my sister succeed to tell the Judenrat that we are on the Palestinian list.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The-- in order to have a value, you-- there were three steps that had to be accomplished.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "First, you had to get a letter from the Palestinian office in Geneva that you are on the list, which was a [? fake ?] letter that from a Jewish institution.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
